  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add diced Thai chilies and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add dehydrated lemongrass and galangal and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add chicken breast and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add lemon juice, fish sauce, and soy sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add chopped cilantro and basil and stir to combine.",
    "Stir in salted butter and cook until melted.",
    "Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve warm over a bed of greens or noodles."
